152
00:09:11,160 --> 00:09:12,640
<font color=#FFFF00>Ja.</font>
<font color=#00FFFF>- So.</font>

153
00:09:13,480 --> 00:09:14,480
<font color=#00FFFF>Achtung.</font>

154
00:09:14,680 --> 00:09:15,680
