00:17:23,480 --> 00:17:25,040
<font color=#FFFF00>die der Metzger gerne hat.</font>

294
00:17:25,040 --> 00:17:26,240
<font color=#00FFFF>Die höhlst du aus.</font>

295
00:17:26,240 --> 00:17:28,840
<font color=#00FFFF>Und das, was du rausholst,</font>
